 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 02 二维 Poisson 方程的 Jacobi 与 Gauss-Seidel 迭代\n",
    "\n",
    "本 notebook 用有限差分法离散二维 Poisson 方程，分别用 **Jacobi 迭代**、**Gauss-Seidel 迭代** 和 **SOR（超松弛）** 求解，并比较收敛速度。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 方程\n",
    "\n",
    "考虑二维 Poisson 方程 Dirichlet 边值问题：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\begin{cases}\n",
    "-\\Delta u = f, & (x, y) \\in \\Omega = (0,1)^2 \\\\\n",
    "u = g, & (x, y) \\in \\partial\\Omega\n",
    "\\end{cases}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "取 $f(x,y) = 2\\pi^2 \\sin(\\pi x)\\sin(\\pi y)$，$g = 0$。对应解析解为\n",
    "\n",
    "$$u(x,y) = \\sin(\\pi x)\\sin(\\pi y).$$\n",
    "\n",
    "## 有限差分离散\n",
    "\n",
    "取 $N \\times N$ 均匀网格，$\\Delta x = \\Delta y = h = 1/(N-1)$，节点 $(x_i, y_j) = (ih, jh)$。\n",
    "\n",
    "用二阶中心差分：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{u_{i+1,j} - 2u_{i,j} + u_{i-1,j}}{h^2} + \\frac{u_{i,j+1} - 2u_{i,j} + u_{i,j-1}}{h^2} = -f_{i,j}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "整理：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "4 u_{i,j} - u_{i+1,j} - u_{i-1,j} - u_{i,j+1} - u_{i,j-1} = h^2 f_{i,j}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "记 $b_{i,j} = h^2 f_{i,j}$，得到线性方程组 $A u = b$。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 迭代法\n",
    "\n",
    "### Jacobi 迭代\n",
    "\n",
    "$$u_{i,j}^{(k+1)} = \\frac{1}{4}\\left(u_{i+1,j}^{(k)} + u_{i-1,j}^{(k)} + u_{i,j+1}^{(k)} + u_{i,j-1}^{(k)} + b_{i,j}\\right)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "特点：所有节点同时更新，天然可并行。\n",
    "\n",
    "### Gauss-Seidel 迭代\n",
    "\n",
    "$$u_{i,j}^{(k+1)} = \\frac{1}{4}\\left(u_{i+1,j}^{(k)} + u_{i-1,j}^{(k+1)} + u_{i,j+1}^{(k)} + u_{i,j-1}^{(k+1)} + b_{i,j}\\right)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "特点：使用最新值，串行更新，收敛比 Jacobi 快约一倍。\n",
    "\n",
    "### SOR（逐次超松弛）\n",
    "\n",
    "$$u_{i,j}^{(k+1)} = (1-\\omega)u_{i,j}^{(k)} + \\frac{\\omega}{4}\\left(u_{i+1,j}^{(k)} + u_{i-1,j}^{(k+1)} + u_{i,j+1}^{(k)} + u_{i,j-1}^{(k+1)} + b_{i,j}\\right)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "最佳松弛因子：$\\omega^* = \\frac{2}{1 + \\sin(\\pi h)}$（理论值）。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 收敛性\n",
    "\n",
    "- Jacobi 迭代矩阵谱半径 $\\rho_J = \\cos^2(\\pi h) \\to 1$（$h \\to 0$）\n",
    "- Gauss-Seidel 谱半径 $\\rho_{GS} = \\cos^2(\\pi h) = \\rho_J^2$\n",
    "- SOR 谱半径 $\\rho_{SOR} = \\omega - 1$（$\\omega = \\omega^*$ 时）\n",
    "\n",
    "所以 SOR 收敛速度比 Jacobi 快 $O(N)$ 倍。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from matplotlib import cm\n",
    "\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 问题设置"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "N = 41                  # 网格点数（含边界）\n",
    "h = 1.0 / (N - 1)       # 网格间距\n",
    "x = np.linspace(0, 1, N)\n",
    "y = np.linspace(0, 1, N)\n",
    "X, Y = np.meshgrid(x, y, indexing='ij')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 源项 f(x,y) = 2π² sin(πx) sin(πy)\n",
    "f = 2 * np.pi**2 * np.sin(np.pi * X) * np.sin(np.pi * Y)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 右端 b = h² f\n",
    "b = h**2 * f\n",
    "\n",
    "# 解析解\n",
    "u_exact = np.sin(np.pi * X) * np.sin(np.pi * Y)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'N = {N}, h = {h:.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'理论 Jacobi 谱半径: {np.cos(np.pi * h)**2:.6f}')\n",
    "print(f'理论 Gauss-Seidel 谱半径: {np.cos(np.pi * h)**4:.6f}')\n",
    "print(f'最佳 SOR 松弛因子: {2 / (1 + np.sin(np.pi * h)):.6f}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
